SummaryEnglish: Physical education is about nurturing one's physical abilities to keep fit and enjoy a lifetime of sports. In other words, phys ed makes life more fun! The super cyborg, Fizz Edward was created by a genius doctor who forgot to program him with phys ed abilities. With "Pro Tips" from top athletes, Fizz Ed learns "Improvement Points" so he can enhance his physical ability.

1.SummaryEnglish: Come see in an easy-to-understand manner "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" on the basic pullover move done on bars.

2.TitleEnglish: Today's Mission is Straddle & Squat Vault!

3.TitleEnglish: Today's Mission is Forward & Backward Roll!
3.SummaryEnglish: Come check out "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" on basic mat exercises: the forward roll and the backward roll.

4.SummaryEnglish: Come check out "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" that will help you jump hurdles with confidence and rhythm.

5.SummaryEnglish: Come and learn "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" that will help you properly kick off and move your body through the air.

6.SummaryEnglish: Come learn "Pro Tips" for double unders, which involves having a jump rope pass under your feet twice in one jump. We'll also go over "Improvement Points" so that you don't get the rope caught on your feet!

7.SummaryEnglish: Come learn "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" on sprinting, including correct posture, line of sight, swinging your arms and elbows, moving your feet, and how to sprint without injury.

8.SummaryEnglish: Come check out "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" on how to catch, throw and dodge the ball.

9.SummaryEnglish: Karate is a traditional sport of Japan. Come learn "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" on the basics of stance, block, kick and punch.

10.SummaryEnglish: Breaking is included as a new event in the 2024 Olympic Games. Come learn "Pro Tips" and "Improvement Points" that will help you bust a move!
